I hadn't the power to keep my lord
out of harm's way...

rows.label: tlk20010151_02_msg0002
rows.name: I must become stronger, for his sake.

rows.label: tlk20010151_02_msg0003

I hope one day to master a skill that
would help with exploration. Scaling
sheer cliff faces, for instance...
